{"tid":193854,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"人越大，越唔敢開口發誓","createTime":"2017-04-09T14:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T14:20:40.000Z","uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"583ad9326c25214728ee28bf86400a20e28a1cc8","tid":193854,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"以前細蚊仔時，隨便同老母講話如果我偷糖食就天打雷劈死無全屍，氹到老母信之後轉個頭就偷粒糖食到津津有味。嗰時真係夠膽隨口發毒誓噏到有幾毒得幾毒都唔怕，最緊要令人信自己，覺得根本破咗個誓都冇後果。<br />\n<br />\n人大咗，講完大話之後唔知點解忽然唔再敢舉起三隻手指親口發誓，哪怕講嘅報應只係今晚跌銀包都唔敢，好怕真係破咗誓會有報應，更唔洗講發毒誓。<br />\n<br />\n人地唔信你，叫你發誓，真係收曬皮。<br />\n<br />\n係咪人大咗睇得社會事多而不自覺變得迷信？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人一樣係咁？"},{"pid":"89888badbb171818551f06c3363f0fa80c0fdb5b","tid":193854,"uid":23296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:36:55.000Z","msg":"人愈大愈怕死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc632c001d66d3698f6731341b4d8e0d0a9c307","tid":193854,"uid":73109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:42:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7134bf230ed506e73e378f370fecdd4271f8fb44","tid":193854,"uid":59268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:50:40.000Z","msg":"人愈大 發誓先易過食生菜<br />\n今日今時太均真 慘過被雷劈呀"},{"pid":"55737d505937a8addb278789164a920962c3ed20","tid":193854,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:20:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人越大唔係應該覺得呢個世界冇報應先真咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係香港，你睇下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日覺得有錢佬先冇報應。"},{"pid":"32c331912854d531b2fc769e2bee21186ec6edce","tid":193854,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人愈大 發誓先易過食生菜<br />\n今日今時太均真 慘過被雷劈呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你啱，但我近幾年忽然過唔到自己嗰關。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e323b8a0742e95d6ba0b22e5be83f7e227b0f7a5","tid":193854,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:34:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人越大唔係應該覺得呢個世界冇報應先真咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係香港，你睇下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日覺得有錢佬先冇報應。</blockquote><br />\n根本就係"},{"pid":"7d27209a79fe9c0a174489f831ec9d5727e4eac0","tid":193854,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"下<br />\n咩而家有天理嫁咩?"},{"pid":"cbeea2e58f99c306381bb71dcd70be0407763697","tid":193854,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T14:20:40.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"}]}